_sText: = This version has now been replaced by deathrun_iceworld_v2 = deathrun_iceworld_v1beta by 'cS.Metz Information: A snowy deathrun map for all you runners out there. This is my first deathrun map, but I have spent a good few weeks working on it to hopefully bring you a fun and enjoyable map. I've tried to keep the icy theme throughout the map with the traps, endings and secrets, and would love to know what you think of it. Also, if you find any bugs, please report them to me on this website and I shall address them when I can. Please download and enjoy my map and let me know what you and your server communities think of it. Credits: Map design and creation by 'cS.Metz with special thanks to Fibbs and my friends for some trap ideas Map Details: - 15 traps (two skill/random) - 3 standard endings - 2 small secrets - 1 secret ending - AFK Timer (one minute) - Map Timer (five minutes) Update Log: v1beta - Release version
